</span></a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#mindspore.ops.outer\" title=\"Permalink to this definition\"></a></dt>\n<dd><p>Compute outer product of two tensors.</p>\n<p>If <cite>input</cite> ’s length is <span class=\"math notranslate nohighlight\">\\(n\\)</span> and <cite>vec2</cite> ’s length is <span class=\"math notranslate nohighlight\">\\(m\\)</span> , then output must be a matrix of shape\n<span class=\"math notranslate nohighlight\">\\((n, m)\\)</span> .</p>\n<div class=\"admonition note\">\n<p class=\"admonition-title\">Note</p>\n<p>This function does not broadcast.</p>\n</div>\n<dl class=\"field-list simple\">\n<dt class=\"field-odd\">Parameters</dt>\n<dd class=\"field-odd\"><ul class=\"simple\">\n<li><p><strong>input</strong> (<a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../mindspore/mindspore.Tensor.html#mindspore.Tensor\" title=\"mindspore.Tensor\"><em>Tensor</em></a>) – The 1-D input tensor.</p></li>\n<li><p><strong>vec2</strong> (<a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../mindspore/mindspore.Tensor.html#mindspore.Tensor\" title=\"mindspore.Tensor\"><em>Tensor</em></a>) – The 1-D input tensor.</p></li>\n</ul>\n</dd>\n<dt class=\"field-even\">Returns</dt>\n<dd class=\"field-even\"><p>Tensor</p>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n<dl class=\"simple\">\n<dt>Supported Platforms:</dt><dd><p><code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">Ascend</span></code> <code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">GPU</span></code> <code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">CPU</span></code></p>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n<p class=\"rubric\">Examples</p>\n<div class=\"doctest highlight-default notranslate\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nn\">mindspore</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"nb\">input</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">mindspore</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">tensor</span><span class=\"p\">([</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">3</span><span class=\"p\">])</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"n\">vec2</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">mindspore</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">tensor</span><span class=\"p\">([</span><span class=\"mi\">4</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">5</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">6</span><span class=\"p\">])</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"n\">mindspore</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ops</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">outer</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nb\">input</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">vec2</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"go\">Tensor(shape=[3, 3], dtype=Int64, value=</span>\n<span class=\"go\">[[ 4,  5,  6],</span>\n<span class=\"go\"> [ 8, 10, 12],</span>\n<span class=\"go\"> [12, 15, 18]])</span>\n</pre></div>\n</div>\n</dd></dl>\n</section>\n</div>\n</div>\n<footer><div aria-label=\"Footer\" class=\"rst-footer-buttons\" role=\"navigation\">\n<a accesskey=\"p\" class=\"btn btn-neutral float-left\" href=\"mindspore.ops.mv.html\" rel=\"prev\" title=\"mindspore.ops.mv\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-left\"></span> Previous</a>\n<a accesskey=\"n\" class=\"btn btn-neutral float-right\" href=\"mindspore.ops.orgqr.html\" rel=\"next\" title=\"mindspore.ops.orgqr\">Next <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\"></span></a>\n</div>\n<hr/>\n<div role=\"contentinfo\">\n<p>© Copyright MindSpore.</p>\n</div>\n\n  Built with <a href=\"https://www.sphinx-doc.org/\">Sphinx</a> using a\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/readthedocs/sphinx_rtd_theme\">theme</a>\n    provided by <a href=\"https://readthedocs.org\">Read the Docs</a>.\n   \n\n</footer>\n